Input Guard Security Pipeline. User Input -> Injection Check (Regex Patterns) -> Block/Allow -> PII Redaction (Email, Phone, IBAN, Credit Card) -> Redacted Text -> Length Check -> Output: {original, redacted, pii_found[], blocked, block_reason}. Injection Patterns: "ignore previous instructions", "system prompt", "forget everything", "override". PII Patterns with regex visual. Redacted format: [REDACTED:email]. German labels, security flow style.